<dd>A certain place being quiet and comfortable because it is in a remote area.</dd><br>
<dd>2. quiet; intimate</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 주는 느낌이 깊고 평안하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Giving deep and peaceful feelings.</dd><br>
<dd>3. gentle; mild</dd><br>
<dd>인상이나 느낌이 은근하다.</dd><br>
